HEADWORD: Adducible
<hw>Ad*du"ci*ble</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of
being adduced.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Proofs innumerable, and in every imaginable manner diversified,
are <qex>adducible</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>I. Taylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

